		<hr size="1">im a 54(soon 55) froglok paladin on cazic, and was wondering what are your methods to gain and keep agro? </P><P>When im MT i normaly begin with Stun,FoL,Holymight and re-stun when need agro. I also use some disarm but im not very sure if it had sufficient agro to worth it. What about the lvl 9 stun call cease or desist? should i use them instead of the higher one call Stun? <BR>oh and does healing wave(grp heal 120hp) had in any agro?</P><P>thank in advance</P><P>Horgh Solarfall<BR>froglok paladin of the 54th Holyslaughter</P><P><BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=718982" TARGET="_BLANK">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=718982</A></P><P>Message edited by: Abbath (2/24/2004 6:40:09 AM)<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
